'''里约热内卢地铁4号线'''（{{lang-pt|Linha 4 do Metrô do Rio de Janeiro}}）是[[巴西|巴西]]里约热内卢的一条地铁线。<ref name="Rio-stats">{{cite web |url=http://g1.globo.com/rio-de-janeiro/noticia/2016/07/temer-participa-de-inauguracao-da-linha-4-do-metro-no-rio.html |title=Temer participa de inauguração da Linha 4 do Metrô no Rio |publisher=G1 Portal |language=pt |trans_title=President Temer takes part in inauguration of Rio's metro's line four |format=url |date=30 July 2016 |accessdate=2016-07-30 |archive-date=2016-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160803102859/http://g1.globo.com/rio-de-janeiro/noticia/2016/07/temer-participa-de-inauguracao-da-linha-4-do-metro-no-rio.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

4号线于2016年7月30日通车。线路连接西部地区的Barra da Tijuca至[[伊帕内玛|伊帕内玛]]。全部车站位于地下。线路采用了中国长春客车厂所制造的车辆。

